data.description: Exquisite 7-bedroom, 5-bathroom, 3-car garage residence nestled within the prestigious gated community of Meadowood. This home boasts an impressive array of features including elegant 18'' diagonal tile flooring in the main living areas. Enjoy the benefits of Impact Glass and Plantation Shutters throughout, along with recently upgraded garages featuring a sleek Epoxy floor coating. Crown molding graces the living space, complemented by a comprehensive sound system enveloping the entire house. Additional highlights encompass a game room, rejuvenating Jacuzzi SPA, and solar lighting in the backyard. Discover the convenience of two master suites, one on each floor, offering versatile living options. Additonal Lot is available for sale. The kitchen showcases rich wood cabinets, gleaming stainless steel appliances, and a full-service laundry room with a separate laundry tub. The master suite features California closets and a luxuriously upgraded master bath. Additionally, find a remodeled cabana bath and an outdoor kitchen complete with a high-end Memphis Elite Pellet Grill and stainless steel appliances. An inground propane tank is in place for added convenience.
